{"tid":1653381,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你係咪要勇武派埋口罩比你","createTime":"2019-10-14T05:02:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T11:09:20.000Z","uid":195047,"like":38,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"dab9c0bb6f35600c0e6252d0e145ae78550d8eac","tid":1653381,"uid":195047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:02:35.000Z","msg":"條街上面20個得1個戴<br />\n你地所謂和理非係咪連口罩都唔撚敢戴？<br />\n話咩焗 熱 冇用 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屌你老母你做咪有用囉</span><br />\n我為班連付出多啲都唔肯嘅人賭上前途<br />\n已經半隻腳係監獄啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你估你係裁判法院出面嗌兩句可以換返前線嘅前途？<br />\n4個月啦 仲有咩心理關口未過<br />\n講左要嘅係心態 打緊仗 而唔係切蛋糕嗌口號咩花都未開到就打飛機話贏緊<br />\n有時間做偵探查浮屍 屌蛋糕 玩分化割蓆<br />\n自問你做左你可以做嘅野未？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我可以為你地擋子彈<br />\n你地連帶口罩 罷工 遊行 上街帶物資都唔肯</span></span><br />\n都係算<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">到時入獄唔好比我聽到嗌反抗 笑死</span>"},{"pid":"23182a46e0c4df6096c88df7e9577b6a9ac0981f","tid":1653381,"uid":195047,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:02:59.000Z","msg":"反省下啦"},{"pid":"7f3f25cd9aba2374f4027548801c528c54c4baf9","tid":1653381,"uid":195047,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:03:10.000Z","msg":"自問你付出過啲咩"},{"pid":"acc43401afc840528739e1858d9a0e76d1d780dc","tid":1653381,"uid":195047,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:03:32.000Z","msg":"你對唔對得住義士"},{"pid":"9c1dafa7850cb97835ba12fb8da7ad63d83aa6c4","tid":1653381,"uid":195047,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:04:01.000Z","msg":"比我係7 8月離開嘅義士我真係死不瞑目"},{"pid":"ff546cb76597766a7d6df1be8fafca4d151d8870","tid":1653381,"uid":139484,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:04:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓主今晚去唔去"},{"pid":"f9b13d4d8576c618573456ae83b91f6cf376ead0","tid":1653381,"uid":146940,"like":0,"dislike":1